Conditional Constructs
Provide
Ability to control whether a statement list is executed
Two constructs
If statement
if
if-else
if-else-ef
Switch statement
Left for reading
The Basic If Statement
Syntax
if(Expression )
Action
If the Expression is true then 
execute Action
Action is either a single 
statement or a group of statements within bracesExpression
Actiontrue false

